Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Rare opportunity to occupy a property on Mascot's busiest shopping strips!

1111 Botany Road is a free-standing building located on the growing Mascot shopping strip.

The property is a functioning food production facility and is offered with 3 cool rooms and a freezer as well as multiple food preparation areas. There is additional office space to the rear of the building which is accessed via a laneway.

The property has a very high profile being located on one of South Sydney's busiest roads - Botany Road.
